For individual store pages, each page includes curated crates organized by genre, wall picks, and featured bins. JSON-LD structured data (LocalBusiness schema with ItemList and BreadcrumbList) is embedded on every store page. Open Graph and Twitter Card metadata are provided for social sharing.

Store count and inventory data update daily. Visit /explore for the current directory.
